---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
    <section class="section-padding-sm border-b border-gold/10 bg-bronze-950">
        <div class="container-content">
            <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
                <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Community</p>
                    <h1 class="font-display text-display-sm text-parchment sm:text-display-md">
                        Build capability.<br />
                        <span class="text-gold">Live with purpose.</span>
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-gold/50 py-1 pl-6 lg:mt-8">
                    <p class="font-display text-lg italic leading-relaxed text-parchment-300 sm:text-xl">
                        "Excellence is not a single act, but a habit built through consistent, faith-aligned
                        discipline."
                    </p>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding section-surface border-b border-gold/10">
        <div class="container-content">
            <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-parchment sm:text-3xl">The Mission</h2>
                    <div class="divider mt-4 mb-6" />
                    <div class="space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-parchment-300">
                        <p>
                            {siteConfig.name} was not created to make you feel good. It was created to make you
                            capable. Specifically, capable of building the kind of life that aligns with your
                            faith, serves your community, and demands disciplined execution.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Look around you. We are living in an era of unprecedented comfort and unprecedented
                            distraction. The modern world is engineered to hook your attention, weaken your
                            habits, and sediment your ambition. Scrolling, binge-watching, junk food, cheap
                            pleasure — these are not random accidents. They are obstacles in the path of your
                            potential.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Too many Muslims are losing this battle. They are drifting through life, medicating
                            anxiety with cheap entertainment, and wondering why they feel empty despite being
                            comfortable.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Our mission is simple: <strong class="font-semibold text-parchment">To provide the antidote.</strong>
                            We exist to pull you out of the seductive comfort of mediocrity and into the clarity
                            of high performance — rooted in Islamic values, grounded in evidence, and practical in
                            application.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-parchment sm:text-3xl">The System</h2>
                    <div class="divider mt-4 mb-6" />
                    <div class="space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-parchment-300">
                        <p>
                            Motivation is garbage. It is a feeling, and feelings are fickle. You cannot build a
                            legacy on how you feel on a Tuesday morning when it's raining and you're tired.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            The amateur relies on inspiration. The professional relies on systems. A system is a
                            set of behaviors, protocols, and environments that make the desired outcome inevitable,
                            regardless of how you feel.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            {siteConfig.name} is a comprehensive operating system for the Muslim experience. We
                            don't just tell you to "be confident" — we give you specific social scripts and body
                            language protocols that signal competence. We don't just tell you to "get in shape" —
                            we give you the exact training and nutrition frameworks that optimize health within
                            Islamic guidelines.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We break down the vague concept of success into concrete, actionable verticals:
                            Health, Mindset, Social, Wealth, and Skill. Each of these is a machine. You are the
                            mechanic. Our job is to hand you the wrench.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding section-surface-alt">
        <div class="container-content">
            <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
                <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-28 lg:self-start">
                    <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Methodology</p>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-parchment sm:text-3xl">Our Methodology</h2>
                    <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-parchment-300">
                        The algorithm for self-transcendence — how we turn complex problems into habits you can
                        actually maintain.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <article class="card border-l-2 border-l-gold/40 p-6">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-display text-gold/30">01</span>
                        <h3 class="mt-1 font-display text-xl text-parchment">Analyze</h3>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-parchment-300">
                            We strip a problem down to its first principles. We ignore tradition and dogma.
                            We only ask: "What is the biological or psychological mechanism at play?"
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card border-l-2 border-l-gold/40 p-6">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-display text-gold/30">02</span>
                        <h3 class="mt-1 font-display text-xl text-parchment">Optimize</h3>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-parchment-300">
                            We design a protocol to exploit that mechanism. This is where scientific literature
                            meets field testing. We formulate the "Minimum Effective Dose" for maximum results.
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <article class="card border-l-2 border-l-gold/40 p-6">
                        <span class="text-3xl font-display text-gold/30">03</span>
                        <h3 class="mt-1 font-display text-xl text-parchment">Automate</h3>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-parchment-300">
                            We turn the protocol into a habit. We build the environment so that adherence is
                            automatic. Thinking is expensive; habits are free. We make excellence improved.
                        </p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding-sm section-surface border-t border-gold/10">
        <div class="container-content">
            <div class="grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-14">
                <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-parchment sm:text-3xl">
                    Are you <span class="text-gold">capable</span> of more?
                </h2>
                <div class="lg:text-right">
                    <a href="/" class="btn-primary inline-flex">Explore The Protocols</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
